<textBlocks>
	<container id="formVBox">
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="25.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Activity 6: Evaluate Actions">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Workshop participants will continue working in small groups to evaluate the actions identified in the last activity for helping build equitable resilience.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="This activity will help to generate a short list of the most feasible and impactful actions for each area of concern/How might we statement.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="Walkabout.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=" 10 min. Participants do a walkabout of the other groups' proposed actions. They can leave comments using sticky notes.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="Small group evaluation.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=" 15 min. Groups reconvene and evaluate the actions they worked on previously (alternative: switch groups around to work on a different set of actions). Criteria for evaluating them could be: equity, feasibility, and hazard impact (see ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="evaluating actions template"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch5_template_Evaluating_Actions.docx">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=").">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="Make the case.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=" Small groups select their top two actions that best meet these criteria.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="Large group discussion.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=" 30 min. Each group presents their case for why their top two actions are best. Discuss questions such as:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- What are some of the trade-offs we might need to make to implement equitable resilience?">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- Can we modify or combine actions to help them become more equitable, feasible, etc.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="Vote.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=" Each participant votes for their top three choices from #4 (e.g. online polling, sticky dots). Be sure to set expectations about voting: people are stating their preference, but just because and idea got the most votes doesn't automatically mean it will get implemented.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Post-workshop: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="We suggest you continue to get feedback on the action ideas, e.g. via social media, meetings of ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="existing groups">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
	</container>
